title: Ranked and Normal Switch
body:
After over 3000 games played in league of legends i made the mistake of clicking ranked instead of normal.

Please put normal above ranked (Like it was before) so my subconscious does not accidental click it again

Cheers mate.

replies.body: Lmao i did this in the morning i was like wtf why am i in norms?!?!?!?
